[CC continues to be reported in Florida. Because of Hurricane Katrina and
previous storms, Florida citrus growers will continue to see additional
findings of CC. The causal bacterium _Xanthomonas axonopodis_ pv. _citri_
will continue to exacerbate the situation for Florida citrus growers.
